				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The flower merchant out front, selling flowers on the approach to the graveyard, is trying desperately to sell her stock. The only thing of interest besides her being a vendor is to imply that she gets her stock from Jaheira's house and to give the gentlest of nudges that maybe there's something over there."
